snippet.textDisplay:
Sorry but Very Very Weird Song, Is song main coke studio ne itni zada mistakes kese kr di ? Ya maybe this is just an experiment, listing some problems in this song according to me (just an opinion as music is subjective) -

1. Starting main rap was not in correct pitch (i know rap sur main nahi hota but jis ek sur pe hota hai uska music k sath samwad hota hai, vo bilkul nahi tha) 

2. Backing vocals (mukh tant ..) sync main he nahi tha, koi aage gaa raha hai koi piche, ajeeb lga

3. Backing vocals very out of tune, sorry to be this blunt but thoda sa pitch correct kr lete tho better hota, (i know raw rakhne ki try ki hai but zada he ho gaya)

4. Music out of sync with Backing vocals, this was very very disappointing coming from coke studio, muth tant wali lines kahan jaa rahi hain uska music kahan jaa raha hai, koi samwad he nahi tha.

5. Lead vocals completely out of tone and mixing sahi nahi ki hui

(MAI BAHUT CHOTA HUN KI COKE STUDIO PE KOI BHI TIPNI KR PAUN BUT YE COKE STUDIO BHARAT HAI, WHICH IS REPRESENTING INDIAN MUSIC, THO JUST GIVING MY BLUNT OPINION, JISKO MUSIC KI SAMAJH HAI USKO SAMAJ AA JAYEGA MAI KYA BOL RAHA HUN)
